    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"The true crime would be to not finish what we started.\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-prerequisite-strong-\"><strong>Prerequisite:</strong></h5><p>You must have an Intelligence score of 16 or higher.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefit-strong-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>You have taken it upon yourself to evolve the art of ninjutsu. You believe that there is so much more that can be done to improve the effectiveness of ninja arts. You gain an efficient molding from the Ninjutsu specialist class. Additionally, you treat yourself as 1 level tier higher when casting E-rank Jutsu.</p>",
